  "Description": {
    "English": "The geometric heart of this ancient weapon is the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Runic Lens</span>. Its impossible geometry not only concentrates light into a high-powered <span class=\"name name-technology\">Mining Laser</span>, but can also warp the local electromagnetic field so as to render the user <span class=\"name name-stellar\">invisible</span>.<br><br>Powered by <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Carbon-based Elements</span>. Fire the beam with <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>. Select its secondary cloaking function with <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEALTWEAPON</span> and hold <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span> to activate.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">符文棱镜</span>是这种远古武器的几何之心。这种不可思议的形状不仅能够将光线聚焦为大功率<span class=\"name name-technology\">开采激光</span>，同时还能够扭曲周遭的电磁力场，为使用者提供<span class=\"name name-stellar\">隐身</span>的效果。<br><br>通过<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳基元素</span>驱动。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>发射光束。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEALTWEAPON</span>选择次要隐形功能并长按<span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span>激活。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這把古代武器的幾何核心是<span class=\"name name-technology\">符文透鏡</span>。不可思義的幾何形狀不僅能將光線集中形成一道高功率<span class=\"name name-technology\">採礦雷射</span>，也可以扭曲局部電磁場，從而讓使用者<span class=\"name name-stellar\">隱形</span>。<br><br>需要<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳基元素</span>提供動能。按 <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span> 發射光束。按 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEALTWEAPON</span> 選擇次要隱形功能並按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span> 啟動。"
  },
